What I'm going to do in the next
video, and this is where

00:03:58.130 --> 00:04:00.730
if anyone wasn't skipping up to
this point, the next video

00:04:00.730 --> 00:04:02.360
is where they should re-engage,
because we're

00:04:02.360 --> 00:04:06.420
actually going to use these
formulas for the

00:04:06.420 --> 00:04:07.440
best fitting line.

